race.comment: PRIVALOVA (4) is working up to another win. Sat a little wide last time and kept coming to finish off strongly when sixth. Will find this assignment easier and is drawn for the soft run on the inside. Looks a leading player on best. ALL THE WAY BABY (11) should be ready to fire after four runs in and has the blinkers added for this. Expected to do much better. EBONY FIGHTER (3) ran an improved race second-up and will be fitter again. Only try this trip ran well in tougher grade albeit unplaced and looks set to find best form now. HANDY FRIEND (1)  hasn't been far away in the three runs back. Has drawn out but will charge at them late.
